title: 'The Challenge: USA' Episode 9 | Surviving the Challenge
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer and Tyson Apostol break down the latest episode of 'The Challenge.' They talk about the formation and destruction of "The Fab Five" (1:00), the genius of the Connect Four challenge (13:45), and Danny's standout episode (25:09).

Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Tyson Apostol
Producer: Kaya McMullen
